üêç Python Tasks with Dataclasses & JSON

This project shows how to save and load tasks using Python.

What I used

Python

@dataclass

Type hints

JSON

What it does

Reads tasks from a JSON file

Turns them into Python objects

Updates the tasks

Saves them back to JSON

Task model
@dataclass
class Task:
    name: str
    priority: int
    done: bool

Why this is useful

This is how real programs store and manage data, like:

To-do apps

APIs

Backend systems